<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA71">
<l>iṭaṅkai valampuriniṉ ṟārppa verikāṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṭaṅkā roṭuṅkuvitta tāḻi – viṭaṅkālun</l>
<l>tīvā yaravaṇaimēṟ ṟōṉṟa ṟicaiyaḷappāṉ</l>
<l>pūvā raṭinimirtta pōtu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While in the left hand the right-spiralling conch roars constantly, the flame-spitting</l>
<l>discus subdues those who don’t give in – at the time when the Appearance</l>
<l>on the bed [that is] a serpent with poison-spitting fire mouths extends</l>
<l>[his] long flower foot in order to measure the directions.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
